  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0d94\u0dba \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An investigation into a Mahaoya fertilizer scam",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Agriculture, Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera, instructed the Secretary of the Ministry, Mr. Rohana Pushpakumara, to conduct an investigation regarding a urea fertilizer fraud that has occurred in the Ampara Mahaoya area.",
        "This investigation is being conducted regarding a case of a Mahaoya farmer's organization fraudulently selling a stock of urea fertilizer that was given to farmers for distribution to a private businessman.",
        "The Ministry of Agriculture says that the businessman who got the fertilizer has sold the fertilizer to the farmers at a higher price and the police have arrested all those involved in the fraud."
      ],
